		<hr />
		
		
		
		
		<div>One comment i'd like to make about the knock/unlock spell suggestion... i like this idea... i play a wizard and a rogue, and would like trap detection, disarming and unlocking to be a larger part of the game... if casters had unlocking spells, the developers could include more things to unlock… there should be more locked doors and chests requiring lockpicking skill or an unlocking spell to open them… rogues would remain superior in the ability, but have more opportunities to exercise it.<br />
<br />
It would be nice to improve and extend the LDoN concept on trap detection, disarming and unlocking to the rest of the game.<br />
<br />
<br />
(thanks ravi - post below - amended the top post to include the link)</div>
