		<hr />
		
		
		
		
		<div>Where did these ideas come from?  (link please)  It would have been better to just reply with your summary to the original thread.<br />
<br />
While some of the ideas seem fair, many of them wouldn't make any sense being in the hands of Wizards.<br />
<br />
Anyways, I'll add my one dream spell to the list:  A Lure-based stun.  I don't care if it has a long recast timer, I don't care if it does any damage.  I just want a stun spell that works on high level mobs that is Lure based for emergency use, and to provide us more versatility.  I miss using stun spells, but at high levels they rarely land and it is very hard to justify the aggro they generate when you could simply be burning the mob down with a regular nuke.</div>
	</td>
</tr>
</table>
