		<div>A long time ago I already offered the possibility to create Runes by a combination of research and pottery.<br />
<br />
- Enchanted clay sculpted into a Runeshape with a mana potion appropiate for the spell level mana requirement.<br />
- Unfired blanco rune is scribed with a rune symbol by combining the unfired blanco rune with the spellscroll and required components in a lexicon.<br />
- Fire rune in a kiln to create a non stackable (No-Drop?) version clickable rune that is charged with 1 charge of that spell. <br />
<br />
Considering the price and amount of mana needed to make the mana potions (enchanter spell line) We would be able to create 1 charge gates, 1 charge nukes, 1 charge whatever spell. As long as it is a Magical spell (WIZ NEC ENC MAG). (Not the Divine Lines CLR DRU SHM)  Some could even be class only, can't have wizards with Mage pets. Although, having a Resurection Rune on you (Necro) would be fun, especially if you failed 10 EE's on the preliminary combines.</div>
